{"tid":133008,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"收回引退宣言 宮崎駿被爆料正在製作長篇動畫","createTime":"2017-02-24T08:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T09:15:20.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ded44fbbd1e020482dbb2fb4aa59707163c19ed","tid":133008,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T08:56:41.000Z","msg":"約三年半前製作完長篇動畫《風起》後，宣布退休的日本動畫大師宮崎駿，曾說不會再製作長篇作品，不過吉卜力工作室的製作人鈴木敏夫爆料，宮崎駿正在製作新的長篇動畫作品，實質上算是收回引退宣言。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n據《日刊體育》報導，鈴木敏夫在美國出席「Oscar Week 2017」活動時表示，宮崎駿已經開始在畫新作品「目前依然努力的在東京製作新作」。宮崎駿在2013年9月時，以年齡已大集中力衰退為由，在公開《風起》後宣布引退，表明不會再製作長篇動畫作品，如今宮崎駿正在製作新的長篇動畫作品，實質上算是收回引退宣言。"},{"pid":"ec3e90445d140153e82b011695587a9af53e0f46","tid":133008,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T08:58:36.000Z","msg":"死老坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肯收檔未"},{"pid":"eb881afb44cc6f65ecc8871f49054c016e0c0c52","tid":133008,"uid":5858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:02:25.000Z","msg":"真 引退<br />\n真 終極 引退<br />\n真 終極 究極 引退<br />\n唔好意思 我唔引退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbcc453d5b71e0b3bd47cb38128e238c589f1499","tid":133008,"uid":47475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:07:58.000Z","msg":"old news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79d09d7f73f10128ac9ae0406bc20bc7923a1fc","tid":133008,"uid":2022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:08:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1da346029fa71374dabedd42c657b09bc51b1851","tid":133008,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:12:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>old news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170224/1063534/收回引退宣言　宮崎駿被爆製作長篇動畫中\" data-sr-url=\"https://